Demi Lovato and Wilmer Valderrama Reunite for Cutest Photo 1 Year After Split

It’s been a year since Demi Lovato and Wilmer Valderrama called it quits and the two are still the cutest. The 24-year-old pop star and the 37-year-old That ’70s Show alum and…
